query:
SELECT 
  tr.id,
  tr.employeeId,
  tr.testId,
  tr.status,
  tr.completedAt,
  tr.score,
  e.email,
  e.name
FROM testResults tr
LEFT JOIN employees e ON tr.employeeId = e.id
WHERE e.email = 'rodrigo.goncalves@uisa.com.br'
ORDER BY tr.createdAt DESC
LIMIT 5;
